oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sound Effects for Chet Atkins
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recordings are a variety of sound effects recorded for Chet Atkins' (musician) use on tracks. The recordings are from an unidentified recorder and date.
